headline: Wells Fargo Launches $20 Million Open for Business Growth Program
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, May 14, 2025--Wells Fargo & Company (WFC) today announced Open for Business Growth, a new $20 million philanthropic program where nonprofits enable small business owners ready to scale operations or grow revenue. Launching first in Chicago, the program will expand to other markets across the U.S. in the coming year.
